'''Engineering''' is one of the most popular majors among [[List of universities in Taiwan|universities in Taiwan]]. The engineering degrees are over a quarter of the bachelor's degrees in Taiwan. Because high-technology manufacturing is the main industry in Taiwan, there are many career opportunities for engineering majors in the country.<ref>{{cite book|title=Insights from Emergent Education Systems in Selected Countries|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wwtiAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA83|year=2011|publisher=Lulu.com|isbn=978-1-105-04314-7|page=83}}</ref>{{Self-published inline|date=December 2017}}
